Detailed Description

A protocol which specifes an interface for sorted sets.

Enumeration Type Documentation

enum CHSubsetConstructionOptions

These constants are passed to -[CHSortedSet subsetFromObject:toObject:options:] and affect how the subset is constructed.

You can pass 0 to use the default behavior.

Enumerator:
CHSubsetExcludeLowEndpoint 

Indicates that a subset should exclude the low endpoint if it is not nil.

CHSubsetExcludeHighEndpoint 

Indicates that a subset should exclude the high endpoint if it is not nil.
